{
  "stem": "12674.5",
  "chunk_idx": 16,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Anyway, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] so that, that was Theresienstadt.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "You worked.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "In the evening you went for a walk.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Once a week you went to the coffee house.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But there were, of course, a lot of things going on that were not-- people would read books.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Somebody that spoke Czech knew the guy that was living across the road outside of town because he was a cousin of his brother-- of his brother-in-law's shoemaker or something.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So you know, people would thing-- there were all these moats and underneath passages.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "People would smuggle things in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "People would smuggle things out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was a child.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I, I didn't know anybody.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I learned the language, but I didn't speak it really, so I wasn't involved in all of this.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But there were things.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There were-- you know, you heard things, and, and things went on one day after the other.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You did what you had to do.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And whenever anybody--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And Mr.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Ram ?] sometimes there were special appells.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know, maybe they wanted to make us feel miserable, or maybe they-- you know, where they would line everybody up and you had to be counted.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he would-- he would come out there and he would stand there and he would scream.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He says, all you people have in your head is how to fill your bellies and how to get out of here.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I can promise you, you're never going to get out of here.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Apropos never getting out of here, my father was working in a carpentry shop, and he managed to have my brother with him.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And at that point--",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
